Regirock (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0376: Metagross
Pokémon
#0378: Regice →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Regirock (TCG Pocket).

Regirock has been featured on 15 different cards since it debuted in the EX Hidden Legends expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Regirock cards are normally Fighting-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Regirock

Regirock
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
